exercises.description:
Create RBAC manifests for a multi-tenant HPC Kubernetes cluster. Define:
(1) a Role named 'ml-developer' in namespace 'ml-training' that allows
full CRUD on pods, jobs, and configmaps, plus read-only on deployments;
(2) a RoleBinding that binds the 'ml-team' group to this role;
(3) a ResourceQuota limiting the namespace to 16 GPUs, 64 CPUs, 256Gi memory.

